It doesnâ€™t demand technique or discipline; it simply asks for space.
When you give it that space, it returns clarity, balance, and resilience.
When you neglect it, the entire system fills with noise.
It is the simplest form of prevention, and one of the most underestimated.

Nutrition â€” 10â€“11%
Explanation:
Nutrition remains one of the most influential preventive components because it shapes every system of the body â€” energy, immunity, 
